## 🔄 Evaluator 통합

### Expression::Identifier 처리

기존 v14.3에서 Identifier를 처리하지 않았으므로 추가합니다:

```rust
pub enum Expression {
    Literal(i32),
    FloatLiteral(f64),
    Identifier(String),          // ← 추가
    Prefix { operator, operand },
    Infix { left, operator, right },
    Grouped(Box<Expression>),
}
```

### Statement 추가

변수 선언을 위해 Statement를 정의합니다:

```rust
pub enum Statement {
    Let {
        name: String,
        value: Expression,
    },
    Expression(Expression),
}
```

### Evaluator 수정

```rust
impl Evaluator {
    pub fn eval_statement(
        &self,
        stmt: &Statement,
        env: &mut Environment,
    ) -> Object {
        match stmt {
            Statement::Let { name, value } => {
                let val = self.eval_expression(value, env);
                if !val.is_error() {
                    env.set(name.clone(), val.clone());
                }
                val
            }
            Statement::Expression(expr) => {
                self.eval_expression(expr, env)
            }
        }
    }

    pub fn eval_expression(
        &self,
        expr: &Expression,
        env: &Environment,
    ) -> Object {
        match expr {
            Expression::Identifier(name) => {
                env.get(name)
                    .unwrap_or_else(|| {
                        Object::Error(format!("undefined variable: {}", name))
                    })
            }
            // ... 기존 Expression 처리 ...
        }
    }
}
```

